{"tid":2366041,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中国天津車廠發生爆炸　至少1死7傷","createTime":"2021-01-14T08:11:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T10:05:38.000Z","uid":184679,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"d9456f1182d5359e5bb1c48397d016d28f740f93","tid":2366041,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T08:11:46.000Z","msg":"內媒報道指，天津港保稅區周四（14日）有工廠發生爆炸，事故目前至少造成1人死亡，7人受傷。截至下午3時半，消防表示現場搜救已結束，無被困人員，正在調查事故起因。<br />\n<br />\n該市應急管理局表示，天津港保稅區捷喜愛汽車零部件有限公司的廠房，在周四12時50分左右發生爆炸。事故發生後，濱海新區應急管理局、保稅區消防救援支隊已立即趕赴事故現場救援。<br />\n<br />\n網傳片段顯示，爆炸產生大量碎片，現場一片狼藉、煙霧瀰漫；有目擊者表示，爆炸發生時，玻璃窗戶被震碎，大量不明物從天而降。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hk.on. cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20210114/bkn-20210114151116652-0114_00952_001.html</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Ju5WfQtGKBc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJu5WfQtGKBc&d=qXcR1A%2FTALq%2FhnoNE0cJVcsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=eee412e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Ju5WfQtGKBc</a>"},{"pid":"97c2ff14a2161d232764dbe4ad6769b11f0af694","tid":2366041,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T08:13:09.000Z","msg":"乜嘢叫「大量不明物從天而降」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe1a94effb18aec4fac2ddecd50cc5393748dcfd","tid":2366041,"uid":133806,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T08:13:28.000Z","msg":"咁少咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c179a3213e967af8a8a8c098af6c61dd3d26771b","tid":2366041,"uid":377847,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T08:14:24.000Z","msg":"可惜咁少"},{"pid":"6b1f6a2a54535aed459e99254eb8221f1df3a843","tid":2366041,"uid":137159,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"97c2ff14a2161d232764dbe4ad6769b11f0af694","tid":2366041,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T08:13:09.000Z","msg":"乜嘢叫「大量不明物從天而降」<img src=\"/assets/faces/no